herbe
------------------------------------------
Daemon-less notifications without D-Bus

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.0-0.212.g6af8fea4bbad
  libX11_6-1.8.9-1
  libXft2-2.3.7-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  libX11-devel-1.8.9-1
  libXft-devel-2.3.7-1
  libfreetype-devel-2.13.3-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/dudik/herbe

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/dudik/herbe/archive/refs/tags/1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack herbe-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./herbe-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/herbe-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/herbe-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(herbe)
  /usr/bin/herbe.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/herbe.README
  /usr/share/doc/herbe/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/herbe/README.md

------------------

Port Notes:

